{"type": "article", "id": 29781, "title": "这家日本旅馆虽小，但宣扬的是整个小镇的魅力", "description": "它带你发现街道和本地的风土。", "date": "2016-07-18T23:13:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3001, "name": "民宿"}, {"id": 7137, "name": "东京"}, {"id": 20433, "name": "旅馆"}, {"id": 30319, "name": "Hanare"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 273, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160718233930OCjnMAtRUYucq9JS.jpeg", "contents": "<p class=\"\">          </p><p>          </p><p><a href=\"http://hanare.hagiso.jp/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hanare</a> 是日本东京谷中的一家旅馆，说它是民宿也许更加贴切。它由两幢当地使用了 50 年的老房子改建而成，一幢是客房，上下两层一共 5 间日式套间，另一幢是公共区 <a href=\"http://hagiso.jp\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hagiso</a>，有售卖咖啡、提供早餐的地方，也可以办会谈活动或画廊。</p><p>这五个客房面积都大概有 10 平方米，保留了传统日式的木结构和榻榻米，一侧墙面悬挂着衣架、毛巾等生活物品，其余就没有多余的东西。卫生间和洗漱室分别在该楼层另外一个房间里，以实现干湿分离。而这个房间分别有五个不一样的名字，Yatsude、Kasumi、Hikari、Kumo 和 Konoha（檀香、霞、光、云、木叶），名称的特征大概就体现在玻璃窗上，细微的花纹产生了这样的效果。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718234154NPWFh1CD56yVLpsd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665833\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">旅馆外观（住宿区）</div></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718235648e3BTfYtLGpqVywEk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">门</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718234723Rw9fA3H6uioIjP7V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.426003\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">一楼二楼平面图</div></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><p class=\"\">两盏灯、两床被子、两张窗帘和一些零碎的毛巾就构成了房间的全部。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607182343019XVKBJEFA8qb3yCH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718234301DRzTt9OlgFZpuiM2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718234343rR15zV0Bu8fUSehy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718234247sVmHqRBbn5Ld7gvD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.618333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718234301eZjczGpm8HwfA3rU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">洗漱间</div></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718235018kJ7oBe1ltPqxgVpZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">水池</div></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718234512QXisvUojLJ5AWr6H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">五种玻璃窗</figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718234521AzkZJgpoftHD5bBy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718234512FUgh2GKy1PTiHIMp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718234512CnrlzWLR2eswEYAy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718234514bPEsCL9DoTa6XAnK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>旅馆在介绍时贴心地提醒“楼梯很陡峭，如果有大的箱子或小孩，适合住在一楼”。</p><p class=\"\">另一幢楼在住宿区的不远处，是由同一家建筑事务所 <a href=\"http://studio.hagiso.jp/work/archi/hagiso/\" rel=\"nofollow\">HAGI STUDIO </a>改建的，他们就在 Hagiso 的二楼办公。这里集中了商店、餐饮、展览和工作室等多个功能，还能为驻地艺术家提供场所，是一个很有文化情调的地方，此外，热闹的公共区与需要安静的住宿区分开，也能照顾更多人休息。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718234905N2YW4srXIxo5tOwZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">旅馆外观（公共区）</div></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718235056aLiewxRg2kVHdy3A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.555858\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718235004r6M2gIhFayjAwmfn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">前台</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718234946CTL1dqUyxVzr5i0P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">餐厅</div></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718235110GxB4QIlLO0nUtXEH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">商店</div></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718234947ZMQiG4f6nIbkx1LE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">咖啡吧</div></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719000134wR8rKAz2ZDvM0Qal.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">展览区</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718235047bUa2FoptE7qefGYS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><p>不过，Hanare 真正的特色是它的地图，每一位登记入住的旅客都能获得一张小镇的地图，有白天和夜晚两个版本，可以寻找到更多的民宿、公共浴室、餐厅、自行车租借处、有名的景点以及可以去体验当地文化的地方(旅馆本身附送门票)。Hanare 认为这些都是旅馆的一部分，名称“hanare”在日语中是离开的意思，就是希望客人可以发现小镇的魅力。</p><p class=\"\">入住一晚约 14040 日元（887.7 人民币），相当于民宿房间的价格。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718235442DZAVr1K9wE7kFaWz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718235454O6mn0Neur1Zj7Hyf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719000342Q0eKWbMORt4DNES8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718235507LX43lcytOU8EFod0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718235545ROclVBHrtGpwx9IJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666923\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><p class=\"\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.everydayobject.us/2016/07/15/hanare-hotel-tokyo/\" rel=\"nofollow\">everydayobject</a>、<a href=\"http://hanare.hagiso.jp/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">hanare</a></p>"}